overview: Air hostesses.... On Dorcel Airlines flight, they are not only beautiful but especially eager to experience sex and pleasures with passengers and crew! Let's get to know Natacha, Marika, Sophia, and also the nymphomaniac blond-haired Nathalie. Stops in hotels' crew are pretexts for special invitations. Passengers and colleagues are welcomed in the rooms to discover the private charms of the air hostesses....pretty tits, wet pussies, and even anuses. Dorcel Airlines proposes the best menu ever seen in a flying company! An exciting journey, between heaven and earth, where fantasies are becoming true.
tagline: At Dorcel Airlines We Aim To Please. Traveling Has Never Felt So Good.
title: Dorcel Airlines: Flight DP69
